  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nFor initial sync, right now we are filtering peers based on its static data: supported protocols, latest status. We should be able to filter them by based on the sync history we worked with them. \r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nAfter we fetch block chunks, we need to track who imported which blocks. We can consider removing peer's supportedProtocols or disconnect it if:\r\n+ Calling `beacon_blocks_by_range` to a peer returns multiple errors\r\n+ Or if peer returns incorrect blocks\r\n\r\nAlso we can track which peers we work the most, how many successful sync times etc...\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\n\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\n",
